metadata.title: Grateful Dead Live at Winterland Arena on 1977-12-31
metadata.creator: Grateful Dead
metadata.description:
Set 1

The Music Never Stopped, Tennessee Jed, Finiculi Finicula, Me & My Uncle, Loser, Jack Straw, Friend Of The Devil, Lazy Lightning-> Supplication

Set 2

Sugar Magnolia-> Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain, Truckin'-> Wharf Rat-> Drums-> Not Fade Away-> Around & Around, E:One More Saturday Night-> E: Casey Jones

Other artist(s): NRPS

metadata.notes:
Notes:
- Thanks to Matt Smith for the transfer
- Thanks to Charlie Miller for coordinating this effort
- Typical of a New Year's show, there are some minor pops/hand claps and whatnot throughout
- Level fluctuations smoothed
- Pitch corrected
- 1st Audience source in circulation for this date (2/18)

Mastered by Scott Clugston
February 8, 2018
